Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾以为你一生的故事是由此刻开始\N{\fs36}I used to think this was the beginning of your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆真是玄妙\N{\fs36}Memory is a strange thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其运作之道远远超出我的想象\N{\fs36}It doesn't work like I thought it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们囿于狭义的时间\N{\fs36}We are so bound by time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,习惯将记忆顺成一条线\N{\fs36}by its order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 妈妈抱\N{\fs36}Okay, come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到妈妈这儿来\N{\fs36}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈抱着你 \N{\fs36}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来\N{\fs36}Stick 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这个小镇的警长吗\N{\fs36}Are you the sheriff in this here town?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的"痒痒枪" 我来抓你啦\N{\fs36}These are my tickle guns, and I'm gonna get ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs36}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我追你吗 快跑哇\N{\fs36}You want me to chase you? You better run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得其中的一些片段\N{\fs36}I remember moments in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs36}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨你\N{\fs36}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一生的故事在此刻完结\N{\fs36}And this was the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到妈妈这儿来\N{\fs36}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别离开妈妈\N{\fs36}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如今 我不知道纠结于开头和结尾还有没有意义\N{\fs36}But now I'm not so sure I believe in beginnings and endings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有些决定你命运的日子 其意义超越了生命本身  \N{\fs36}There are days that define your story beyond your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如它们降临的那一天\N{\fs36}Like the day they arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fs36}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 早  - 早\N{\fs36}- Morning. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人都哪儿去了\N{\fs36}Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 上课\N{\fs36}Okay. Well, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们来谈谈葡萄牙语\N{\fs36}Today, we are talking about Portuguese
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说为什么它的发音与别的罗曼语族大不相同\N{\fs36}and why it sounds so different from the other Romance languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葡萄牙语起源于加利西亚自治区王国\N{\fs36}The story of Portuguese begins in the kingdom of Galicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不好意思  - 在中世纪\N{\fs36}- Sorry. - ...in the Middle Ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,语言被视为一种艺术的表达形式\N{\fs36}where language was seen as an expression of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么新鲜事要跟大家分享吗\N{\fs36}Any news you wanna share?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks博士 您能打开电视 调到新闻频道吗\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks, can you turn the TV to a news channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已抵达现场\N{\fs36}...arrived here on scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但警方已事先在这周围设置了路障\N{\fs36}but police have already set up a blockade here around the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到 我们已经尽可能地靠近现场\N{\fs36}As you can see, we've gotten just about as close as we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是 此刻蒙大拿州已经被全面封锁\N{\fs36}but unfortunately, Montana, right now, is on complete lockdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据悉\N{\fs36}The object apparently
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该物于40分钟前在94号州际公路北侧着陆\N{\fs36}touched down 40 minutes ago just north of I-94.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在等待确切消息\N{\fs36}We're waiting to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来判断该物是试验飞船还是\N{\fs36}if this is perhaps an experimental vessel or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fs36}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚得知已经有更多类似物体\N{\fs36}I'm learning that more objects like this have landed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全球范围内其他八个地点着陆\N{\fs36}at as many as eight other locations around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有视频资料吗 我们能播吗 \N{\fs36}Yes. Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您眼前所见的画面来自北海道的一个网站\N{\fs36}This is from a site in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一次全球性事件 此刻仍在进行中\N{\fs36}This is worldwide. It is happening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 下课\N{\fs36}That's... Class is dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 我们只希望大家能多配合 \N{\fs36}For now, we're simply asking for cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该物将交由有关部门进行评估\N{\fs36}while authorities assess the object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你是说它不是我们国家的吗\N{\fs36}So, you're saying it's not ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底能不能确定它是否来自地球呢\N{\fs36}Do you even know if it's from Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在搜集信息\N{\fs36}We're still collecting information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也在和其他国家商讨\N{\fs36}We're coordinating with other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是唯一迎来不速之客的国家\N{\fs36}We are not the only ones to have one of these in our backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是某种象征和平的"第一类接触"\N{\fs36}If this is some sort of peaceful first contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一下子送来12个\N{\fs36}why send 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1个不就够了吗\N{\fs36}Why not just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道 我也看到了\N{\fs36}Yeah, I know. I saw that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 妈 我跟你看的是一样的报道\N{\fs36}I don't know, Mom. I'm watching the same news coverage you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 妈 那个频道就别看了好吗\N{\fs36}Well, Mom, please don't bother with that channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要我跟你说多少次啊 那些人都是白痴\N{\fs36}How many times do I have to tell you those people are idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 那你觉得我听起来紧张吗\N{\fs36}Yeah, well, do I sound nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那不就得了\N{\fs36}Okay, exactly. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗 嗯 你知道的 还是老样子\N{\fs36}Me? Yeah. You know me, I'm about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈 我很好\N{\fs36}Mom, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 再联系 再见\N{\fs36}Okay, I'll call you later. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这些物体着陆近八小时后\N{\fs36}And at around eight hours after landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}第一类接触 泛指人类与外星生物的第一次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍未出现任何"第一类接触"的迹象\N{\fs36}there are still no signs of what might be called "First contact."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到 这些物体至少有1500英尺高\N{\fs36}Now, the objects measure at least 1, 500 feet tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有报道称其中有两个侵入了俄罗斯领空\N{\fs36}Two are reported to have penetrated Russian airspace,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个位于西伯利亚 另一个位于黑海沿岸\N{\fs36}one in Siberia and the other off the coast of the Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悬浮在海面上\N{\fs36}...suspended above the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,截至目前\N{\fs36}So far, there are 12
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全球范围内已出现12个不明物体\N{\fs36}unidentified objects spread across the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其停驻地点间并无明显逻辑关联\N{\fs36}There is no obvious logic to their locations
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无迹象表明这些船只内有\N{\fs36}and no evidence that the ships are even...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个大胆设想 如果它确是某种飞船\N{\fs36}...who entertain the idea that if it is a kind of vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这种飞船或许是无人驾驶的\N{\fs36}it may be unmanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 我们有一套针对此类事况的章程 只是\N{\fs36}Regardless, we have a protocol for scenarios like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在经历了周二的非常事件后\N{\fs36}After Tuesday's extraordinary events,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统于今晨宣布国家进入紧急状态\N{\fs36}the President, this morning, has declared a state of emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 5000名国家警卫队成员\N{\fs36}with as many as 5, 000 National Guard being deployed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将被派遣至蒙大拿州\N{\fs36}to the state of Montana alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边境已被封锁 航班全数停运\N{\fs36}Borders are closed and flights have been grounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致数百万旅客滞留\N{\fs36}stranding millions of travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因恐慌而哄抢汽油 饮用水和食物的现象不断恶化\N{\fs36}Panic buying of gas, water, and food continues to escalate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦当局已临时解除\N{\fs36}and federal authorities have temporarily lifted all caps
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对执法部门的加班时长的限制\N{\fs36}on overtime for law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒精烟草枪械管理局已不再下发新的持枪许可证\N{\fs36}The ATF has put a temporary ban on new gun licenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫使众多经营狩猎器材和枪械的个体商户\N{\fs36}forcing many independent suppliers of hunting equipment and firearms
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭门歇业 不再对公众开放\N{\fs36}to close their doors to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距12个不明飞行物的出现已经48小时了\N{\fs36}Forty-eight hours later and no further development...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才两天\N{\fs36}Two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍未有新的进展\N{\fs36}...from the sight of the 12 UFO...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公众就指望我们能知道所有答案\N{\fs36}And already the public expects us to know the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是G.T. Weber上校\N{\fs36}I'm Colonel G.T. Weber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从没正式见过面\N{\fs36}We never formally met,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过两年前\N{\fs36}but two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给陆军情报处提供了一些波斯语翻译吧\N{\fs36}you did some Farsi translations for Army intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些叛乱视频你翻译得很快\N{\fs36}You made quick work of those insurgent videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些叛乱人员你处理得也很快\N{\fs36}You made quick work of those insurgents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有涉及翻译方面的问题\N{\fs36}You are on the top of everyone's list
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们都会第一个想到你\N{\fs36}when it comes to translations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:27.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}SSBI 是就职政府顶级机要部门需要接受的一种单一领域背景调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你之前的单一领域背景调查还有两年有效期\N{\fs36}And you have another two years in the SSBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你仍有接触最高机密的权限\N{\fs36}So, you still have top-secret clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我来你办公室 而没去伯克利的原因\N{\fs36}That's why I'm in your office and not at Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个东西 需要你帮我翻译\N{\fs36}I have something I need you to translate for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么来这里\N{\fs36}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你们能听得懂我们说的话吗\N{\fs36}Can you... Can you understand us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们从哪里来\N{\fs36}Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这些\N{\fs36}Now you heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看\N{\fs36}What do you make of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是\N{\fs36}Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs36}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有几个\N{\fs36}How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个什么\N{\fs36}How many what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有几个在说话\N{\fs36}How many speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个\N{\fs36}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设当时它们不是同时发声的话\N{\fs36}Assume they were not speaking at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗 它们有嘴吗\N{\fs36}Are you sure? Did they have mouths...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么翻译\N{\fs36}How would you approach translating this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有听出任何单词\N{\fs36}Do you hear any words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者短语吗\N{\fs36}Phrases?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不 我不知道\N{\fs36}I don't... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你能告诉我什么\N{\fs36}So, what can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能告诉你的是\N{\fs36}I can tell you that it's
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单凭一个音频文件是无法实现翻译的\N{\fs36}impossible to translate from an audio file.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到现场和它们互动\N{\fs36}I would need to be there to interact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你翻译波斯语的时候也没去现场啊\N{\fs36}You didn't need that with the Farsi translations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我会说波斯语\N{\fs36}I didn't need it because I already knew the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这个 这是\N{\fs36}But this, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想干什么\N{\fs36}I know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那你倒是说说看  - 我是不会带你去蒙大拿的\N{\fs36}- Tell me what I'm doing. - I'm not taking you to Montana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能 否则那里就会变成旅游景点\N{\fs36}It's all I can do to keep it from turning into a tourist site
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个有最高机密权限的人都会跑去一游\N{\fs36}for everybody who has a TS clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在告诉你如何才能完成这份工作\N{\fs36}I'm just telling you what it would take to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没得商量\N{\fs36}This is not a negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一走 你就会失去这个机会\N{\fs36}If I leave here, your chance is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fs36}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校\N{\fs36}Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才提到伯克利 接下来是要去那找Danvers翻译吗\N{\fs36}You mentioned Berkeley, are you going to ask Danvers next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:13:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\fs36}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你敲定他之前\N{\fs36}Before you commit to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问问他梵语里的"战争"是哪个词 作何解\N{\fs36}ask him the Sanskrit word for "War" And its translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚 随着俄罗斯和中国加入联合国会谈 \N{\fs36}An agreement on sharing scientific discoveries looks closer tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各国将有望达成一项协定 共享科研成就\N{\fs36}as Russia and China join talks at the United Nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时 全球金融市场陷入危机\N{\fs36}Meanwhile, financial markets across the world are in crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道琼斯工业指数暴跌2000点\N{\fs36}as the Dow Jones Industrial Average fell over 2,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破其单周跌幅最高记录\N{\fs36}in its worst weekly decline in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早\N{\fs36}Mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校好\N{\fs36}Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}梵语中有多个表达"战争"的词 "Gavisti"并非最贴切的词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他选了Gavisti这个词 他说是"争论"的意思\N{\fs36}Gavisti. He says it means "An argument."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个词你怎么解\N{\fs36}What do you say it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"对更多牛的渴望"\N{\fs36}"A desire for more cows."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾行李吧\N{\fs36}Pack your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 给我20分钟可以吗\N{\fs36}All right, give me 20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们10分钟内起飞\N{\fs36}We take off in 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks博士 这边请\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks. Right this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接完毕 准备前往\N{\fs36}Contact and ready to approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见谅 Banks博士 我检查一下你的安全措施\N{\fs36}Excuse me, Dr. Banks, let me make sure you're properly secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\fs36}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢提醒\N{\fs36}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 你刚才说的我没听清\N{\fs36}Sorry, I couldn't hear what you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"语言是文明的基础"\N{\fs36}"Language is the foundation of civilization."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"它是凝聚一个民族的粘合剂"\N{\fs36}"It is the glue that holds a people together."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"也是产生冲突时最先出鞘的武器"\N{\fs36}"It is the first weapon drawn in a conflict."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise 这位是Ian Donnelly\N{\fs36}Louise, this is Ian Donnelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是Louise Banks 他是Ian Donnelly\N{\fs36}Louise Banks, Ian Donnelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开场白很精彩啊\N{\fs36}It's quite a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 引用了你的大作\N{\fs36}Yeah. Well, you wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但\N{\fs36}Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,序言一般都得这么写\N{\fs36}It's the kind of thing you write as a preface,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花式下定义 吸引注意力\N{\fs36}dazzle them with the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 句子很优美\N{\fs36}Yeah. It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但话说错了\N{\fs36}Even if it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了吗\N{\fs36}It's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文明的基石\N{\fs36}Well, the cornerstone of civilization
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是语言 是科学\N{\fs36}isn't language, it's science.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ian是洛斯阿拉莫斯国家实验室的理论物理学家\N{\fs36}Ian is a theoretical physicist from Los Alamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向我汇报工作\N{\fs36}You'll be reporting to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在"壳"里的时候 你要和他搭档\N{\fs36}but you'll be working with him when you're in the shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"壳"是他们给不明飞行物起的代号\N{\fs36}That's what they're calling the UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首要任务是搞清楚 它们要什么 它们从哪儿来\N{\fs36}Priority one. What do they want, where are they from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次是 它们怎么来这里的\N{\fs36}And beyond that, how did they get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们有进行超光速旅行的能力吗\N{\fs36}Are they capable of faster-than-light travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们\N{\fs36}Are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我列了一张问题清单 我们可以按顺序问\N{\fs36}I have a list of questions that, you know, we can go over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从"交流"二进制数列开始\N{\fs36}Starting with a series of just a "Handshake" of binary sequences...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如从谈话开始吧\N{\fs36}How about we just talk to them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急着砸一堆数学题\N{\fs36}before we start throwing math problems at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是请你们一起过来的原因\N{\fs36}This is why you're both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带着咖啡的\N{\fs36}I'll bring the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和外星人喝咖啡\N{\fs36}Coffee with some aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把这两位带到Kettler医生那里\N{\fs36}All right. I want you to take these two to Dr. Kettler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命 长官\N{\fs36}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着这位上尉去医务室\N{\fs36}Follow the captain to Medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花几分钟走个程序\N{\fs36}The procedure should take just a few minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我们就开始工作\N{\fs36}and then, we'll get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李交给这几位吧\N{\fs36}These men are gonna take care of your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机交给我保管\N{\fs36}I'll take your cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机给我\N{\fs36}Cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fs36}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个戴上 你们得一直戴着\N{\fs36}Put these on. You're gonna wear them at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他们来了再说  - 好\N{\fs36}- Not until they're here. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 他们来了\N{\fs36}Sir, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise Banks和Ian Donnelly吗\N{\fs36}Louise Banks? Ian Donnelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们上一次进食是什么时候\N{\fs36}When was the last time either of you have eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 昨晚  - 我也是\N{\fs36}- Last night. - Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们上一次感受到压力是什么时候\N{\fs36}When's the last time you did something stressful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在算吗\N{\fs36}Does now count?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说说而已\N{\fs36}Just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抬进救援直升机的是谁啊\N{\fs36}Who was being carted off in the medevac?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是所有人都能承受得住这番经历的\N{\fs36}Not everyone is able to process experiences like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你们抽点血\N{\fs36}I'm gonna get some blood from you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再给你们打一针疫苗\N{\fs36}and give you an immunization dose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵御细菌入侵感染\N{\fs36}that covers a battery of bacterial threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把这些文件签了 好吗\N{\fs36}Would you sign these, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把袖子卷起来\N{\fs36}And roll up your sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:20:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们谁患有幽闭恐惧症吗\N{\fs36}Either of you claustrophobic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没有  - 没有\N{\fs36}- Nope. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近在服用药物吗 有过敏史吗 怀孕了吗\N{\fs36}Currently taking any medications? Allergies? Pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs36}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强效疫苗对人体作用力很猛 \N{\fs36}The booster is a kick to your system,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可能会出现一些副作用\N{\fs36}so you may experience some side-effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如恶心 眩晕 头痛\N{\fs36}nausea, dizziness, headaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵里出现像耳鸣一般的嗡嗡声\N{\fs36}a ringing in your ears like you have tinnitus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到他怎么了吗\N{\fs36}You see what's happening to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这究竟怎么回事\N{\fs36}How does this even work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读数没有变化 但是\N{\fs36}The readings do not change, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 我们就像是爬在纸上的虫\N{\fs36}I don't know. It's like we're insects on a piece of paper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们轻飘飘地把我们扫地出门了\N{\fs36}and they're easing us out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在112分钟19秒那一刻\N{\fs36}At exactly 112 minutes and 19 seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力出现变化 我们就滑了出去\N{\fs36}the gravity starts to shift and slides us out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事儿你找到一个科学的解释了吗\N{\fs36}Have you found a scientific explanation for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 是出自它们的需要吗\N{\fs36}Like, is it for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我觉得是为了我们\N{\fs36}No, we think it's for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交流舱内的空气好像并不能流通\N{\fs36}The air doesn't seem to circulate inside the chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大约两小时后 氧气就耗尽了\N{\fs36}so after about two hours, you run out of oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把新鲜空气泵入房间用不着18小时啊\N{\fs36}It doesn't take 18 hours to pump fresh air into a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大气\N{\fs36}Atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs36}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它们的大气与地球的不同\N{\fs36}If their atmosphere is different from Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定需要好几个小时\N{\fs36}it would certainly take hours to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我们重新平衡氧气的含量和压强\N{\fs36}to rebalance the O2 content and pressure for us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每开一次门 它们就要重复一次\N{\fs36}every time they open their door.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照你这么说 它们随时可以让我们窒息而死\N{\fs36}So, you're saying they could suffocate us if they wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是美国中央情报局的David Halpern特工\N{\fs36}This is Agent David Halpern with the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带两位去你们的岗位吧\N{\fs36}Let me get you two to your stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 长官\N{\fs36}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住 我们需要尽快得到答案\N{\fs36}Remember, we need answers as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们要什么 它们从哪儿来 它们为什么来这儿\N{\fs36}What do they want, where are they from, why they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是首要任务  - 明白\N{\fs36}- This is the priority. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家注意 这是Ian Donnelly博士\N{\fs36}Everyone, this is Dr. Ian Donnelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将负责管理这个团队\N{\fs36}He'll be running this team here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 它们对什么有过回应吗\N{\fs36}Yeah, have they responded to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}斐波那契数 即黄金分割数列 常见于自然界规律中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如形状 图案 数字 斐波那契数 \N{\fs36}Shapes, patterns, numbers, Fibonacci?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们连它们回应"你好"时说的是什么都不知道\N{\fs36}We can't tell what they are saying when they respond to "Hello,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要操之过急了\N{\fs36}so don't get ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们到底有哪些进展\N{\fs36}What have you figured out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才刚刚开始\N{\fs36}We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 早上好  - 早上好\N{\fs36}- Good morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Louise Banks博士\N{\fs36}This is Dr. Louise Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她将负责管理你们的团队\N{\fs36}She'll be heading your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Banks博士 见到你很荣幸  - 你好\N{\fs36}- Dr. Banks. It's a pleasure meeting you. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks博士将接手Walker博士的工作\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks is taking over the mission from Dr. Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好  - Banks博士 又见面了\N{\fs36}- Nice to see you. - Dr. Banks, glad to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:22:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这警报会在任务开始前15分钟拉响\N{\fs36}That's your 15-minute warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你潜过水吗\N{\fs36}You scuba-dive before?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场环境的辐射很强吗\N{\fs36}What kind of radiation exposure are we walking into?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很弱 装备只是为了安全起见\N{\fs36}Nominal, these are just for safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 会需要身体接触那个 \N{\fs36}So, is there any physical contact with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不出"外星人"的只有我一个人吗\N{\fs36}Am I the only one having trouble saying "Aliens"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一面墙 类似玻璃的墙 你没法接触到它们\N{\fs36}There's a wall, like a glass wall. You can't get to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们长什么样啊\N{\fs36}So, what do they look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快就知道了 快点吧\N{\fs36}You'll see soon enough. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 请走这边\N{\fs36}Thank you. Turn this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各单位注意 随时待命 完毕\N{\fs36}All units, stand by. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始会觉得这套防护服笨重 但你会习惯的\N{\fs36}The suits are clumsy at first, but you get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装到第二辆车上\N{\fs36}Load up in the second vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快点 把它放好\N{\fs36}Hurry up, hurry up. Bring it over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.88,0:23:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们准备好了 长官\N{\fs36}We're clear over here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完毕 长官 这是这辆车上最后一箱了\N{\fs36}All set, sir. This is the last box for this truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:23:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡车装载完毕\N{\fs36}This truck's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发了\N{\fs36}Let's go!
