Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.44,0:37:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类\N{\fs36}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.84,0:38:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到 阿尔法小队\N{\fs36}Affirmative, Alpha...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.08,0:38:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\fs36}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.40,0:38:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们记录下来了吗\N{\fs36}Are you getting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.84,0:38:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 长官 正在将信息传回营地\N{\fs36}Yes, sir. It's uploading back to base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.44,0:38:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.24,0:38:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不可思议了\N{\fs36}That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.88,0:38:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类\N{\fs36}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.48,0:38:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类\N{\fs36}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.08,0:38:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类\N{\fs36}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.76,0:39:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.20,0:39:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 慢慢来 大家伙们\N{\fs36}Okay, slow down, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.52,0:39:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来\N{\fs36}Slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.96,0:39:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想给你泼冷水\N{\fs36}I don't wanna take away from your success in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.48,0:39:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 Banks博士 你这招真的行吗\N{\fs36}but, Dr. Banks, is this really the right approach?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.44,0:39:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试着去教它们怎么说和读\N{\fs36}Trying to teach 'em how to speak and read?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.96,0:39:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定要花好长时间\N{\fs36}That's gotta take longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.43,0:39:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了 这样更快\N{\fs36}You're wrong. It's faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.89,0:39:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在现场的一举一动\N{\fs36}Everything you do in there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.44,0:39:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都得向一屋子的人解释\N{\fs36}I have to explain to a room full of men
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.35,0:39:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他们只关心一个问题\N{\fs36}whose first and last question
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.76,0:39:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这样对我们有什么危害"\N{\fs36}is "How can this be used against us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.11,0:39:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你得详细给我解释一下你的计划\N{\fs36}So, you're gonna have to give me more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.96,0:39:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袋鼠\N{\fs36}Kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.44,0:39:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs36}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.92,0:39:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1770年\N{\fs36}In 1770,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.66,0:39:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库克船长的船在澳大利亚的海岸搁浅\N{\fs36}Captain James Cook's ship ran aground off the coast of Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.80,0:40:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是他带领一行人深入这个地区\N{\fs36}and he led a party into the country
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.19,0:40:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且遇到了当地的土著居民\N{\fs36}and they met the Aboriginal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.48,0:40:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一个船员指着那种跳来跳去\N{\fs36}One of the sailors pointed at the animals that hop around
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.60,0:40:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并把幼崽放在育儿袋里的动物\N{\fs36}and put their babies in their pouch,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.42,0:40:10.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}此处的"kanguru"与英文中袋鼠的发音"kangaroo"相同
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.44,0:40:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问道 那是什么 土著居民说道"Kanguru"\N{\fs36}and he asked what they were, and the Aborigines said, "Kanguru."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.12,0:40:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的重点是什么\N{\fs36}And the point is?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.68,0:40:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到后来他们才了解到\N{\fs36}It wasn't until later that they learned that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.15,0:40:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Kanguru"的意思是"我听不懂"\N{\fs36}"Kanguru" Means "I don't understand."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.60,0:40:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我需要通过读写交流来避免出现这种错误\N{\fs36}So, I need this so that we don't misinterpret things in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.32,0:40:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然会花费比这多10倍的时间\N{\fs36}otherwise this is gonna take 10 times as long.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.76,0:40:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这理由能拖住一阵子\N{\fs36}I could sell that for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.68,0:40:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我需要你在进行下一次会话之前\N{\fs36}But I need you to submit your vocabulary words
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.80,0:40:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提交一份词汇表\N{\fs36}Before the next session.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.52,0:40:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行\N{\fs36}Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.56,0:40:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 别忘了土著居民的下场\N{\fs36}And remember what happened to the Aborigines.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.53,0:40:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个更先进的种族差点将他们消灭\N{\fs36}A more advanced race nearly wiped'em out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.52,0:40:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的故事不错\N{\fs36}It's a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.40,0:40:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.36,0:40:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事是假的\N{\fs36}It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.96,0:40:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但印证了我的观点\N{\fs36}But it proves my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.44,0:41:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像成功从它们那儿\N{\fs36}We think we were able to reproduce
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.40,0:41:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推导出了一些质数数列\N{\fs36}some prime number sequences back at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.12,0:41:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 算是有点进展\N{\fs36}So, that's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.32,0:41:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恭喜了 你成了学舌的鹦鹉\N{\fs36}Well, congratulations. You're a parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.44,0:41:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是很有意义的 你个臭小子\N{\fs36}Well, it's a lot more than that, you cheeky bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.04,0:41:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不懂吗 它们似乎无法理解我们的代数\N{\fs36}Don't you see? They can't seem to follow our algebra.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.40,0:41:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却可以理解更复杂的领域 \N{\fs36}But complex behaviors? That clicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.44,0:41:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不合理啊 是吧\N{\fs36}Well, that doesn't make any sense at all, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.20,0:41:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是 在与外星人坦诚相待的政策上 \N{\fs36}The problem is, not everyone shares our policy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.60,0:41:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是所有人都能和我们达成共识\N{\fs36}of being open with the aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.40,0:41:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道Shang将军吗\N{\fs36}Have you met General Shang?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.90,0:41:50.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}呼号是无线电通信的法定代码 世界范围内具有唯一性
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.92,0:41:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的呼号是"关键牌"\N{\fs36}Call sign for him is "Big Domino."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.44,0:41:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论Shang将军采取什么行动 至少会有四个国家紧随其后\N{\fs36}Whatever Shang does, at least four other nations will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.92,0:41:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Louise 你今天得有新进展  - 好的\N{\fs36}- Louise, you have to gain ground today. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.64,0:41:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你的词汇表准备好了吗  - 准备了\N{\fs36}- You have a vocabulary list for me? - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.04,0:42:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算把你和Ian的名字教给它们吗\N{\fs36}You're gonna teach them your name and Ian's?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.32,0:42:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 这样我们就能知道它们的名字 \N{\fs36}Yes, so that we can learn their names,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.44,0:42:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是它们也有名字\N{\fs36}if they have names,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.29,0:42:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再介绍代词\N{\fs36}and then introduce pronouns later.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.80,0:42:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是小学词汇\N{\fs36}These are all grade-school words.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.00,0:42:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"吃" "走"\N{\fs36}"Eat." "Walk."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.04,0:42:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说为什么要教这些\N{\fs36}Help me understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.56,0:42:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.72,0:42:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 不 别擦上面\N{\fs36}No, no, no, not the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.15,0:42:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这就是你想问清楚的问题 对吧\N{\fs36}Okay, this is where you wanna get to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.28,0:42:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是的没错  - 好的\N{\fs36}- That is the question. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.80,0:42:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 首先我们要保证\N{\fs36}So, first we need to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.12,0:42:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们能够理解什么是"问题"\N{\fs36}that they understand what a question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.68,0:42:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 这是一种请求\N{\fs36}Okay? The nature of a request
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.77,0:42:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得答复信息的句式\N{\fs36}for information along with a response.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.84,0:42:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们应该阐明\N{\fs36}Then, we need to clarify
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.16,0:42:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特称的"你"与群体的"你们"之间的差别\N{\fs36}the difference between a specific "You" And a collective "You,"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.40,0:43:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们不想知道外星人甲来这里干什么\N{\fs36}because we don't want to know why Joe Alien is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.88,0:43:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想知道的是这个群体为何要着陆于此\N{\fs36}We want to know why they all landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.76,0:43:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而"目的"这个词包含对意图的理解\N{\fs36}And "Purpose" Requires an understanding of intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.16,0:43:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要搞清楚 它们能自主做出选择吗\N{\fs36}We need to find out, do they make conscious choices
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.00,0:43:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是它们的动机都只是由直觉驱使\N{\fs36}or is their motivation so instinctive
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.28,0:43:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而无法理解涉及到"为什么"的问题\N{\fs36}that they don't understand a "Why" Question at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.44,0:43:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 最关键的一点是\N{\fs36}And... And biggest of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.99,0:43:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与它们之间要有足够丰富的词汇储备\N{\fs36}we need to have enough vocabulary with them
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.64,0:43:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们才能理解它们的回答\N{\fs36}that we understand their answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.76,0:43:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fs36}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.79,0:43:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就按你的单子来\N{\fs36}Stick to your list.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.12,0:43:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别再补充了\N{\fs36}Just don't add anything to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.88,0:43:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力为0.97 氧气含量为21.4% 完毕\N{\fs36}Gravity, 0.97. Oxygen level, 21.4%. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.60,0:43:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神鹰 阿尔法小队已基本就位\N{\fs36}Condor, Alpha's now in the main.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.92,0:43:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正安置设备和遥测装置 完毕\N{\fs36}Setting up equipment and telemetry. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.40,0:43:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\fs36}Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.08,0:44:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Louise."\N{\fs36}"Louise."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.24,0:44:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise 我叫Louise\N{\fs36}Louise. I am Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.16,0:44:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs36}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.72,0:44:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新的符号吗 我看不出来\N{\fs36}Is that a new symbol? I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.93,0:44:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 我觉得应该还是代表"人类"的那个符号\N{\fs36}I don't know I think it's the symbol for "Human" Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.40,0:44:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是符号尾部卷了一点\N{\fs36}It just has a little curl on the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.80,0:44:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是表示提问\N{\fs36}maybe to indicate a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.76,0:44:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不敢肯定\N{\fs36}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.69,0:44:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好说 Louise\N{\fs36}I don't know, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.36,0:44:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得它们可能被弄糊涂了\N{\fs36}I think they're getting confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.36,0:44:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks博士 也许我们应该继续下一个单词\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks, perhaps we should move on to the next word.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.80,0:45:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks博士\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.80,0:45:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没事的  - 怎么回事\N{\fs36}- It's okay. - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.44,0:45:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿 你在干什么\N{\fs36}Hey, hey, hey. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.64,0:45:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我没事  - 你疯了吗\N{\fs36}- Yeah, I'm fine. - Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.96,0:45:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得让它们看见我\N{\fs36}They need to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.72,0:45:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在脱她的防护服 Banks博士\N{\fs36}She's taking off her hazmat suit. Dr. Banks!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.84,0:45:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗\N{\fs36}Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.12,0:45:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样有接触污染的危险\N{\fs36}You're risking contamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.20,0:45:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得让它们看清我的样子\N{\fs36}They need to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.56,0:45:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks博士\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.28,0:45:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks博士\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.08,0:45:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她朝玻璃屏走过去了\N{\fs36}She's walking towards the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.28,0:45:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要中止任务吗\N{\fs36}Should we abort?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.96,0:45:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求收到 等待蓄意杀伤指令\N{\fs36}Request noted. Stand by for frag order.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.64,0:45:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到你们的原位\N{\fs36}Go back to your stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.32,0:46:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下算是正式介绍了\N{\fs36}Now that's a proper introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.72,0:46:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.16,0:47:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Louise."\N{\fs36}"Louise."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.44,0:47:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Louise\N{\fs36}I am Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.02,0:47:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ian 你想做个自我介绍吗\N{\fs36}Ian, you want to introduce yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.18,0:47:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.54,0:47:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.38,0:47:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他的\N{\fs36}Screw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.62,0:47:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人固有一死 对吧\N{\fs36}Everybody dies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.50,0:47:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 Donnelly要脱掉他的防护服\N{\fs36}Sir, Donnelly is taking off his hazmat suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.30,0:47:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否中止任务\N{\fs36}Permission to abort?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.34,0:47:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续执行\N{\fs36}Continue the session.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.10,0:47:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ian\N{\fs36}Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.86,0:48:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.06,0:48:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N{\fs36}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.90,0:48:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁\N{\fs36}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.66,0:48:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜这是它们的名字\N{\fs36}I think those are their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.18,0:48:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们有名字\N{\fs36}They have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.34,0:48:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们要怎么称呼它们呢\N{\fs36}So, what are we gonna call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.90,0:48:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs36}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.40,0:48:50.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}<两傻双人秀>主演Abbott和Costello 是上世纪40年代到50年代好莱坞一对著名喜剧搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.42,0:48:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想叫它们Abbott和Costello\N{\fs36}I was thinking Abbott and Costello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.54,0:48:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.94,0:48:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 可以吗  - 好啊 我喜欢这两个名字\N{\fs36}- Yeah? - Yeah, I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.30,0:49:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢\N{\fs36}I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.46,0:49:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一小队 请下车\N{\fs36}Team 1, exit your vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.46,0:49:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻前往消毒棚\N{\fs36}and proceed directly ahead to the decontamination tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.46,0:49:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达设备间之前请勿摘除防毒面具\N{\fs36}Leave your respirator on until you reach the equipment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.14,0:50:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs36}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.30,0:50:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二小队 请下车\N{\fs36}Team 2, exit your vehicles
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.27,0:50:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并立刻前往消毒棚\N{\fs36}and continue to the decontamination tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.06,0:50:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请勿摘除防毒面具\N{\fs36}Leave your respirators on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.66,0:50:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达设备间之前请勿逗留\N{\fs36}and do not hesitate until you reach the equipment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.34,0:50:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\fs36}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.62,0:50:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精疲力尽\N{\fs36}Overworked.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.70,0:50:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不用我多说你也明白\N{\fs36}Well, I guess I don't need to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.92,0:50:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以身涉险了\N{\fs36}you're putting yourself at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.42,0:50:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时没有辐射中毒的迹象\N{\fs36}There are no signs of radiation poisoning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.26,0:50:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的验血结果出来后 我们再复查\N{\fs36}We'll see how your blood tests look.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.78,0:50:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这儿再给你打一针强效疫苗\N{\fs36}For now, I'm gonna give you another boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.70,0:50:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.10,0:50:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没测出辐射\N{\fs36}No radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.70,0:50:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没测出任何异常\N{\fs36}Nothing else we can detect either,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.38,0:50:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是建议给他们各打一针全效疫苗\N{\fs36}but I'd give'em a strong cocktail regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.94,0:50:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们第一次取得突破性进展\N{\fs36}It's the first time we've made significant progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.06,0:50:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs36}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.26,0:50:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这风险我们担了\N{\fs36}We'll take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.70,0:50:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好了 亲爱的  - 那边到底什么情况\N{\fs36}- Okay, honey... - What is going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.62,0:51:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的  - 能给我露点口风吗\N{\fs36}- Honey. - Is there anything you can tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.22,0:51:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能 但你不用担心 好吗\N{\fs36}No... You don't need to worry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.22,0:51:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我怎么能不担心  - 冷静点\N{\fs36}- How can I not worry? - Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.70,0:51:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一下\N{\fs36}Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.66,0:51:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Becky问我 那些怪物会不会杀了爸爸\N{\fs36}Becky asked me if the monsters are going to kill Daddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.82,0:51:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 不会的\N{\fs36}Honey, it's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.10,0:51:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要保重\N{\fs36}Just stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.74,0:51:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心\N{\fs36}You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.06,0:51:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你保重 我好害怕\N{\fs36}Please, I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.10,0:51:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体初级外星语言学家和科研人员\N{\fs36}All junior xenolinguistics and science personnel
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.66,0:51:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须遵守通用宵禁守则 如无指挥官特许\N{\fs36}must observe general curfew unless expressly authorized
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.10,0:51:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请勿超时工作\N{\fs36}for extended work hours by unit COs.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.86,0:51:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宵禁每晚10点起生效\N{\fs36}Curfew in effect as of 2200 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.02,0:51:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体加班人员 消防人员 守夜人员请注意\N{\fs36}Notice to all late workers, fire watchers and night staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.22,0:51:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即刻起 将通宵供应夜宵\N{\fs36}Effective immediately, midnight rations will be served all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.98,0:52:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七肢桶带来了太多未解之谜 以下只是冰山一角\N{\fs36}Here are some of the many things we don't know about heptapods.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.82,0:52:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在希腊语中 Hepta表示"七" Pod表示"脚"\N{\fs36}Greek. Hepta, "Seven. " Pod, "Foot."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.34,0:52:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"七只脚" 是七肢桶名字的由来\N{\fs36}"Seven feet." Heptapod.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.34,0:52:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是谁\N{\fs36}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.10,0:52:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企图有理有据地解答这个疑问的尝试\N{\fs36}Trying to answer this in any meaningful way
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.54,0:52:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被一个事实所击败\N{\fs36}is hampered by the fact that,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.30,0:52:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是尽管我们可以看得到 听得到七肢桶\N{\fs36}outside being able to see them and hear them,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.74,0:52:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它们却从未留下任何可追踪的痕迹\N{\fs36}the heptapods leave absolutely no footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.74,0:53:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不知道它们宇宙飞船的化学成分\N{\fs36}The chemical composition of their spaceship is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.02,0:53:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那"壳"状的飞船没有废料 未曾排气 也无辐射\N{\fs36}The shell emits no waste, no gas, no radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.14,0:53:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是这些飞船之间存在沟通的渠道\N{\fs36}Assuming that the shells communicate with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.90,0:53:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是无从探测 无迹可寻\N{\fs36}they do so without detection.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.10,0:53:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这些飞船附近的空气\N{\fs36}The air between the shells
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.78,0:53:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有受声波或光波干扰的痕迹\N{\fs36}is untroubled by sonic emission or light wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.70,0:53:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们究竟是科学家还是观光客\N{\fs36}Are they scientists or tourists?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.50,0:53:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是科学家 为什么它们甚少发问\N{\fs36}If they're scientists, they don't seem to ask a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.90,0:53:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么它们会选择在这些地方停驻\N{\fs36}Why did they park where they did?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.54,0:53:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界最负盛名的专家们都毫无头绪\N{\fs36}The world's most decorated experts can't crack that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.06,0:53:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最靠谱的解释是 它们选择的这些地方\N{\fs36}The most plausible theory is that they chose places on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.26,0:53:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是地球上遭到雷击可能性最小的地方\N{\fs36}with the lowest incidence of lightning strikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.06,0:53:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其中仍有个别例外\N{\fs36}But there are exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.98,0:53:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次靠谱的解释\N{\fs36}The next most plausible theory
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.24,0:53:46.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}西娜·阿斯顿 80年代英国的流行乐天后 其热门单曲曾蝉联世界各地的排行版单
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.21,0:53:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提出80年代歌手西娜·阿斯顿的单曲\N{\fs36}is that Sheena Easton had a hit song
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.58,0:53:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经在这些地点成为大热门 实在是牵强附会\N{\fs36}at each of these sites in 1980. So, we just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.74,0:53:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们如何沟通呢\N{\fs36}How do they communicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.26,0:53:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise在这方面的研究成果 让我们都自叹不如\N{\fs36}Here, Louise is putting us all to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.38,0:53:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个重大突破\N{\fs36}The first breakthrough
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.34,0:54:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们发现了\N{\fs36}was to discover that there's no correlation
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.10,0:54:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七肢桶的口语和文字之间没有关联\N{\fs36}between what a heptapod says and what a heptapod writes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.38,0:54:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与人类所有的书面语言不同\N{\fs36}Unlike all written human languages,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.85,0:54:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的文字是会意象形的语标式文字\N{\fs36}their writing is semasiographic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.18,0:54:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种文字能表意 但是无对应发音\N{\fs36}It conveys meaning. It doesn't represent sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.62,0:54:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许在它们看来 我们的文字形式反而是多此一举\N{\fs36}Perhaps they view our form of writing as a wasted opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.82,0:54:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪费了建立另一种沟通渠道的机会\N{\fs36}passing up a second communications channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.82,0:54:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要感谢巴基斯坦的朋友们\N{\fs36}We have our friends in Pakistan to thank
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.76,0:54:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们对七肢桶的书写方式做了研究\N{\fs36}for their study of how heptapods write.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.78,0:54:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与口语不同 标记文字不受时间的束缚\N{\fs36}Because, unlike speech, a logogram is free of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.66,0:55:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如七肢桶的飞船和身体一样\N{\fs36}Like their ship or their bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.18,0:55:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的书面语言并无先后顺序之分\N{\fs36}their written language has no forward or backward direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.06,0:55:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,语言学家称之为"非线性拼写"\N{\fs36}Linguists call this "Nonlinear orthography,"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.30,0:55:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不禁引发了疑问"它们的思维方式也是如此吗"\N{\fs36}which raises the question, "Is this how they think?"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.86,0:55:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假使你要用双手来写一个句子\N{\fs36}Imagine you wanted to write a sentence using two hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.62,0:55:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两只手同时从两端落笔\N{\fs36}starting from either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.34,0:55:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不仅得想好句子中的每一个词\N{\fs36}You would have to know each word you wanted to use
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.14,0:55:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要先预计每个词所占用的空间\N{\fs36}as well as how much space that it would occupy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.90,0:55:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对七肢桶来说 写一句复杂的句子\N{\fs36}A heptapod can write a complex sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.10,0:55:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需两秒 不费吹灰之力\N{\fs36}in two seconds, effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.30,0:55:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们用了一个月的时间 才写出一句最简单的回应\N{\fs36}It's taken us a month to make the simplest reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.74,0:55:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 我们要扩充词汇量\N{\fs36}Next, expanding vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.58,0:55:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise认为至少还要一个月\N{\fs36}Louise thinks it could easily take another month
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.58,0:55:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能准备充分\N{\fs36}to be ready for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.30,0:55:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs36}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.10,0:56:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs36}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.22,0:56:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Weber在找你呢\N{\fs36}Weber's looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.02,0:56:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 不然我干嘛藏在这儿呢\N{\fs36}Yeah, well, why do you think I'm hiding out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.92,0:56:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上来吧\N{\fs36}Come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.42,0:56:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs36}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.58,0:56:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs36}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.94,0:56:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这外面很美吧\N{\fs36}Nice out here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.30,0:56:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 景色不错\N{\fs36}Yeah, it's a nice view.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.94,0:56:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远离喧嚣\N{\fs36}Away from the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.90,0:56:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才正想着你\N{\fs36}You know, I was just thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.70,0:56:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你处理语言的方式就像个数学家\N{\fs36}You approach language like a mathematician.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.90,0:56:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂我的意思吗\N{\fs36}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.54,0:56:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就当你是在夸我了\N{\fs36}I will take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.02,0:56:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实是在夸你\N{\fs36}Yeah, well, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.58,0:56:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实\N{\fs36}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.90,0:56:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带着我们躲开了沟通交流的误区\N{\fs36}I watch you steer us around these communication traps
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.54,0:56:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前对这些根本一无所知\N{\fs36}that I didn't even know existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.58,0:56:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总在想"这也行啊"\N{\fs36}It's like "What"?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.34,0:56:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这就是我单身的原因吧\N{\fs36}I guess that's why I'm single.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.38,0:56:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我 就算深谙沟通之道\N{\fs36}Trust me, you can understand communication
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.62,0:57:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一样可能孤独终老\N{\fs36}and still end up single.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.62,0:57:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那里发生的一切\N{\fs36}I feel like everything that happens in there
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.18,0:57:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终都取决于我们俩\N{\fs36}comes down to the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.82,0:57:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这应该算好事啊 靠你和我的话\N{\fs36}Yeah, it's a good thing though, right? You and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.02,0:57:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们一起工作的那帮废柴你也看到了吧\N{\fs36}Have you seen the jokers that we're working with?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.82,0:57:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好和我搭档的是你\N{\fs36}I'm glad I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.06,0:57:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚 第一张外星人的照片被疯传\N{\fs36}Tonight, the first photograph of the aliens goes viral.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.78,0:57:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,环保团体声称蒙大拿的飞船降临点\N{\fs36}Biological contamination is a major risk factor at the Montana site,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.66,0:57:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面临"生化污染"的重大危机\N{\fs36}so say environmental pressure groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.02,0:57:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八十万民众走上华盛顿街头\N{\fs36}Eight-hundred thousand march on Washington
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.18,0:57:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗议政府对危机的处理不力\N{\fs36}to protest the government's handling of the crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.90,0:57:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上及更多专题报道敬请关注\N{\fs36}All this, and more special coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.12,0:58:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管那玩意儿里面到底是什么 \N{\fs36}First contact with whoever it is that is inside that thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.82,0:58:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁在安排第一次接触 是政府\N{\fs36}and who do we have running the show? The government.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.78,0:58:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 大伙儿们 就是这个政府\N{\fs36}That's right, folks. The same government
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.82,0:58:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁了我们的医疗保险 还把我们的军队搞破产了\N{\fs36}who ruined our healthcare and bankrupted our military.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.66,0:58:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这些人\N{\fs36}Look at these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.74,0:58:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数甚至都没有配枪\N{\fs36}Most of them don't even have guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.86,0:58:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很可能将遭受一场全面入侵\N{\fs36}We could be facing a full-scale invasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.06,0:58:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们的总统却还能坐得住\N{\fs36}and our president is just willing to sit back
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.06,0:58:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放任它们从天而降 占山为王\N{\fs36}and let them waltz in and take our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.06,0:58:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大难当头 我们还蒙在鼓里啊 同胞们\N{\fs36}We are falling asleep at the wheel, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.54,0:58:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们明白我的意思 你们懂的\N{\fs36}You know what I'm talking about. I know you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.50,0:58:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 我们最明智的做法\N{\fs36}What if the smartest thing we could do right now
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.86,0:58:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是出动武力震慑吗\N{\fs36}would be to give them a show of force?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.98,0:58:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给它们一次警告\N{\fs36}I'm talking about a shot across the bow
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.14,0:58:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道你们是怎么想的\N{\fs36}I wanna hear what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.22,0:58:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首位来电观众 你的电话接通了\N{\fs36}Caller number one, you're on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.63,0:58:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对整件事有何高见\N{\fs36}What do you think about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.03,0:59:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么词\N{\fs36}What's this word?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.96,0:59:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"行星"\N{\fs36}"Planet."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.26,0:59:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\fs36}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.18,0:59:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 地球是一个行星\N{\fs36}That's, like... The Earth is a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.96,0:59:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看看我在Garriott老师课上做得作业吗\N{\fs36}Want to see my project from Miss Garriott's class?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.26,0:59:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 小鼻怪\N{\fs36}Yeah, little nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.18,0:59:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得编一集我们自己的电视节目\N{\fs36}We had to make up our own TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.93,0:59:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是假设我们有这么一档栏目的话\N{\fs36}If we had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.22,0:59:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那两个人是谁  - 是你和爸爸\N{\fs36}- And who are those two people? - That's you and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.60,0:59:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节目的名字叫<妈妈爸爸与动物谈话>\N{\fs36}The show is called Mommy and Daddy Talk to Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.56,0:59:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画得真可爱\N{\fs36}Well, it's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.53,0:59:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.78,1:00:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你因为爸爸妈妈的事情而难过 没关系的\N{\fs36}You know it's okay to be sad that your dad and I...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.08,1:00:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我不难过\N{\fs36}I know. I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.75,1:00:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都很爱你\N{\fs36}'Cause we both love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.71,1:00:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 只是把你们画在一起 不是真的要你们一起\N{\fs36}I know. It's just a cartoon. Not real.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.56,1:00:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.47,1:00:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs36}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.44,1:00:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.51,1:00:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还好\N{\fs36}Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.39,1:00:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事情 我也不知道怎么解释\N{\fs36}I'm not sure it's something I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.12,1:00:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上一次找Kettler医生体检是什么时候\N{\fs36}When was your last checkup with Dr. Kettler?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.20,1:00:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fs36}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.12,1:00:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去透透气\N{\fs36}I'm gonna get some air.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.40,1:00:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的\N{\fs36}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.64,1:00:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 我很好\N{\fs36}- All right. - I'm fine. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.52,1:01:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\fs36}How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.36,1:01:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得补补觉 不过我没事\N{\fs36}I need some sleep, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.88,1:01:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.52,1:01:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近读到的一个理论中提到\N{\fs36}You know, I was doing some reading about this idea that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.90,1:02:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过全身心的投入研究一门外语\N{\fs36}if you immerse yourself into a foreign language,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.20,1:02:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可以实现思维重构的\N{\fs36}that you can actually rewire your brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.99,1:02:06.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}萨佩尔-沃尔夫假说又称"语言相对论" 提出在不同文化下 不同的语言在很大程度上影响了使用者的思考方式 即语言决定人的思维
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.00,1:02:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 这是萨佩尔-沃尔夫假说\N{\fs36}Yeah, the Sapir-Whorf Hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.72,1:02:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个理论它\N{\fs36}The theory that...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.72,1:02:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它讲得是\N{\fs36}It's the theory that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.80,1:02:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所讲的语言决定了你思考的方式\N{\fs36}the language you speak determines how you think and...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.48,1:02:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 语言会影响你对一切事物的感知\N{\fs36}Yeah. It affects how you see everything. It was...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.56,1:02:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点好奇\N{\fs36}I'm curious,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.16,1:02:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做梦的时候 也说它们的语言吗\N{\fs36}are you dreaming in their language?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.40,1:02:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能是做了几个梦 但是我没有\N{\fs36}I may have had a few dreams, but I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.76,1:02:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并没有影响到我工作的能力\N{\fs36}I don't think that that makes me unfit to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.76,1:03:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡过觉了么\N{\fs36}Did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.52,1:03:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了一会儿\N{\fs36}A little.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.40,1:03:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会汉语么\N{\fs36}Do you know Mandarin?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.00,1:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标在移动\N{\fs36}It is shifting.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.48,1:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你马上要听到的这个声音来自中方军事首脑\N{\fs36}The voice you're about to hear belongs to China's military chief,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.40,1:03:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shang将军\N{\fs36}General Shang.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.76,1:03:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调出来\N{\fs36}Pull it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.04,1:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有我们收到的卫星讯息 他正在和某个人说话\N{\fs36}We got a satellite feed here of who he's talking to,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.20,1:03:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以边看边听\N{\fs36}if you want to look.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.72,1:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 往回倒\N{\fs36}Wait, go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.72,1:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停 \N{\fs36}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.08,1:03:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说12艘飞船都会提供先进的技术\N{\fs36}He's saying that each of the 12 is offering advanced technology.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.48,1:03:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往回倒 然后播放\N{\fs36}And back again. And play.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.22,1:03:58.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}刻子 麻将术语 指一组三张同样的牌
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.24,1:03:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我们的科研团队正在尝试解码这些组合(刻子)"\N{\fs36}"Our science team is attempting to decode the sets."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.92,1:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"组合(刻子)" 我不知道这是什么意思\N{\fs36}"Sets." I don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.60,1:04:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和占据优势有关\N{\fs36}Something about advantage.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.40,1:04:05.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}花色指麻将中的筒条万 字牌指麻将中的东南西北中发白 花牌指麻将中的春夏秋冬梅兰竹菊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.40,1:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"华裳(花色) 正派(字牌) 还有花(花牌)"\N{\fs36}"Suits, honor, and flowers."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.12,1:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不\N{\fs36}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.84,1:04:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道什么意思 就这些了\N{\fs36}I don't know, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.68,1:04:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道是什么意思\N{\fs36}I don't know what it means either.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.92,1:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个小时前 中方开始集结军队\N{\fs36}An hour ago, China mobilized forces.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.76,1:04:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在俄罗斯也准备跟风出牌\N{\fs36}And now, Russia is following suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.36,1:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shang已经蓄势待发了\N{\fs36}Shang's about to start something.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.60,1:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟风出牌 牌的"花色"\N{\fs36}Following suit, "Suits".
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.76,1:04:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是花色 字牌 花牌\N{\fs36}Suits. Honor. Flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.40,1:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校 这些都是麻将里的牌型\N{\fs36}Colonel, those are all tile sets in mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.96,1:04:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 他们\N{\fs36}God, are they...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.92,1:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是在用游戏和他们的七肢桶交流吗\N{\fs36}Are they using a game to converse with their heptapods?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.64,1:04:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能 怎么了\N{\fs36}Maybe. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.40,1:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如我没有教它们说英语 而是教它们国际象棋\N{\fs36}Well, let's say that I taught them chess instead of English.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.28,1:04:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一场对话都会是一局博弈\N{\fs36}Every conversation would be a game,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.12,1:04:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个想法都出自对立面 不是你赢 就是我输 \N{\fs36}every idea expressed through opposition, victory, defeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.52,1:04:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看出问题了么\N{\fs36}You see the problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.08,1:04:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如授人以锤\N{\fs36}If all I ever gave you was a hammer...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.16,1:04:56.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}出自心理学大师马斯洛 作两解 一是头脑简单的人会滥用手中有限的工具 二是仅熟悉某一物件的人会因为证实性偏差而试图用此物解决一切问题
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.16,1:04:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万物于他皆是钉\N{\fs36}Everything's a nail.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.70,1:05:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须提出那个关键问题\N{\fs36}We need to ask the big question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.96,1:05:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间再铺垫了\N{\fs36}Ready or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.52,1:05:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 那么\N{\fs36}Right, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.64,1:05:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 告诉我你用的什么温度 好吗\N{\fs36}Okay, let me know what temperature you use, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.96,1:05:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这和之前的一样\N{\fs36}No, this is the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.12,1:05:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你看  - 我\N{\fs36}- See. - I...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.80,1:05:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 不 在三和四之间\N{\fs36}Yeah, no, but between three and four.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.28,1:05:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好了 该出发了  - 好\N{\fs36}- All right, time to go. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.96,1:05:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会话剩余时间96分钟 完毕\N{\fs36}Ninety-six minutes remaining in the session. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.56,1:05:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.88,1:05:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七肢桶的目的\N{\fs36}Heptapod's purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.64,1:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七肢桶 目的 地球 你们的目的是什么\N{\fs36}Heptapod purpose. Earth. What is your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.76,1:06:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有Costello来了吗\N{\fs36}Do we only have Costello?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.40,1:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 都来了\N{\fs36}Okay. There you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.52,1:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它说什么\N{\fs36}What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.60,1:06:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"提供武器"\N{\fs36}"Offer weapon."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.00,1:07:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你亲眼看见它们这么写的\N{\fs36}But you saw what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.28,1:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用的是它们没有完全理解的单词\N{\fs36}Using a word they don't fully understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.68,1:07:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这可能只是一个请求  - 或者是警告\N{\fs36}- It could be just a request. - Or a warning.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.16,1:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fs36}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.76,1:07:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.48,1:07:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不知道它们是否明白\N{\fs36}We don't know if they understand
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.60,1:07:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器和工具之间的区别\N{\fs36}the difference between a weapon and a tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.76,1:07:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的语言 和我们的文化一样混乱复杂\N{\fs36}Our language, like our culture, is messy,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.80,1:07:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的时候一词会有多义\N{\fs36}and sometimes one can be both.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.44,1:07:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很有可能它们是想\N{\fs36}I think it's quite possible
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.75,1:07:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们提供一些东西给它们\N{\fs36}that they're asking us to offer them something,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.12,1:07:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是反过来提供给我们 也许这是寻求贸易之举\N{\fs36}not the other way around, like the first part of a trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.56,1:07:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们怎么才能弄清它们的言外之意呢\N{\fs36}So, how do we clarify their intentions beyond those two words?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.92,1:07:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以再回去\N{\fs36}Well, I go back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.32,1:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们立刻回那里去 然后把它弄清楚\N{\fs36}Right away, we go back in and we clear this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.56,1:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这比你想的更复杂\N{\fs36}It's more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.72,1:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么就复杂了\N{\fs36}How is it more complicated than that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.80,1:07:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校 您有来自国防部长的电话\N{\fs36}Colonel, the Secretary of Defense is on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.28,1:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在弄清确切含义之前 我们得封锁这个消息\N{\fs36}We need to sit on this information till we know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.76,1:07:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能冒险分享给我们的敌人\N{\fs36}So, we aren't sharing it with our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.32,1:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还必须考虑一种可能性\N{\fs36}We have to consider the idea
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.72,1:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这些访客是想怂恿我们发动内战\N{\fs36}that our visitors are prodding us to fight among ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.96,1:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直至分出最终胜负\N{\fs36}until only one faction prevails.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.32,1:07:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种说法毫无依据\N{\fs36}There's no evidence of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.56,1:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然有 \N{\fs36}Sure there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.00,1:08:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻翻历史书\N{\fs36}Just grab a history book.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.14,1:08:03.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}英国和德国曾分别殖民印度及卢旺达 并在殖民地开展大屠杀
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.16,1:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英国人对印度 德国人对卢旺达\N{\fs36}The British with India, the Germans with Rwanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.93,1:08:06.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}匈牙利在历史上曾数次被侵略和占领
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.92,1:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在匈牙利 这种事都有了专门的名词\N{\fs36}They even got a name for it in Hungary.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.04,1:08:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.84,1:08:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这个世界 大家各自为政\N{\fs36}We're a world with no single leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.60,1:08:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逐个击破太困难了\N{\fs36}It's impossible to deal with just one of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 "武器"这个词很耐人寻味\N{\fs36}And with the word "Weapon" Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.68,1:08:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Halpern\N{\fs36}Halpern.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.04,1:08:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 长官 \N{\fs36}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.68,1:08:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到 请等待指示\N{\fs36}Copy that. Waiting for instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.60,1:08:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况尚未确认\N{\fs36}No confirmation yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.40,1:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持待命状态\N{\fs36}Standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.20,1:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么情况\N{\fs36}Anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.84,1:08:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底说什么了\N{\fs36}What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.12,1:08:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中国和俄罗斯切断了通讯\N{\fs36}China and Russia are off the grid.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.33,1:08:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不再和任何人交流\N{\fs36}They aren't speaking to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.72,1:08:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道最后一场会话中说了什么 把他们吓到了\N{\fs36}Whatever they learned in their last session has them spooked.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.48,1:09:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\fs36}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.12,1:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们收到命令 和他们一样离线\N{\fs36}We have orders to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.64,1:09:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 这都是我们的盟友啊\N{\fs36}Wait, these are our allies.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.88,1:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校 你不能切断我们的信号\N{\fs36}Colonel, you can't shut us down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.04,1:09:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 开启无线电静默  - 照做\N{\fs36}- Put us on radio silence. - Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.24,1:09:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们收到一则消息是来自七\N{\fs36}We received a message from the He...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.68,1:09:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\fs36}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.72,1:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得保持相互交流\N{\fs36}We need to be talking to each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.08,1:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想和他们交流 先弄清楚这是什么意思\N{\fs36}You wanna talk to them? Find out what this means.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.24,1:09:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,营地通讯已离线 \N{\fs36}Base-camp talk is now offline.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.44,1:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 全体翻译  - 无法确认 他们已经离线\N{\fs36}- All interpreters... - No confirmation. They're offline.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.08,1:09:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止工作并向各小组协调员汇报\N{\fs36}...stand down and report to unit coordinators.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.20,1:09:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从来没有去而复返过\N{\fs36}We've never re-entered a session before.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.24,1:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise 相信我好吗 我们还有时间\N{\fs36}Look, Louise, trust me, okay? We've got time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.00,1:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要抓紧一点 好吗\N{\fs36}We've just gotta step on it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.80,1:09:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"使用武器"\N{\fs36}"Use weapon."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.68,1:09:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据称正是这则外星人的讯息\N{\fs36}This is the alien message
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.92,1:09:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,促使中国政府于今日\N{\fs36}said to have provoked the Chinese government
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.92,1:09:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将中方科学家\N{\fs36}to withdraw their scientists
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.50,1:09:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从国际联合行动中撤出\N{\fs36}from the international mission today.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.20,1:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一则声明中 Shang将军表示\N{\fs36}In a statement, General Shang said,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.60,1:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"中国不再相信这些企图分裂人类的外星人"\N{\fs36}"China no longer trusts the aliens who want to divide us."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.08,1:09:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"人类必须受到保护"\N{\fs36}"Humanity must be protected."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.24,1:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中国已向联合国请求召开紧急会谈\N{\fs36}China has asked for immediate talks at the UN.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.40,1:10:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔法19 这里是神鹰 完毕\N{\fs36}Alpha one-niner, this is Condor. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.60,1:10:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔法19 这里是神鹰\N{\fs36}Alpha one-niner, this is Condor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.28,1:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答 完毕\N{\fs36}Come in. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.72,1:10:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marks上尉 这里是神鹰\N{\fs36}Captain Marks, Condor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.40,1:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有收到回应 如果你听到 请回应两声静噪\N{\fs36}Not receiving transmission. Squelch twice if you hear mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.92,1:10:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marks上尉 全体护卫人员\N{\fs36}Captain Marks, all escort groups
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.14,1:10:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受命终止一切活动\N{\fs36}are ordered to cease all activity.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.16,1:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 Banks教授 你不能进来\N{\fs36}No, no, no. Dr. Banks, you can't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.36,1:11:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们问个问题就好\N{\fs36}We just need to ask one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.72,1:11:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks教授 这次会话已经结束了 你不能\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks, the session is finished. You can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.28,1:11:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能进去 里面很危险\N{\fs36}You can't go back in. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.68,1:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只需要五分钟 别担心\N{\fs36}Look, we just need five minutes. Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.48,1:11:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marks 让他们进去\N{\fs36}Marks, let them go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.36,1:11:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Abbott\N{\fs36}Hey, Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.24,1:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这回怎么算 第37次会话吗\N{\fs36}So, what are we calling this, session 37?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.64,1:11:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 第36次 第二部分\N{\fs36}No, 36, part two.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.40,1:11:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs36}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.96,1:11:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.80,1:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就他们两个人\N{\fs36}Why they on their own?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.96,1:11:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在尝试呼叫Marks上尉\N{\fs36}We've been attempting to hail Captain Marks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.00,1:11:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫小组没有回应 长官\N{\fs36}The escort units are not responding, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.88,1:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不回应\N{\fs36}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.24,1:11:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派安保过去\N{\fs36}Send security.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.84,1:11:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"提供武器 问号"\N{\fs36}"Offer weapon. Question mark."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.24,1:11:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是要向我们提供什么吗\N{\fs36}Are you offering us something?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.56,1:12:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"技术 设备 方法"\N{\fs36}"Technology. Apparatus. Method"?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.56,1:12:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你看 这是另一个词\N{\fs36}Yeah, see, this is a different word.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.76,1:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一段要紧凑的多\N{\fs36}This segment, it's a lot busier.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.96,1:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"给予"\N{\fs36}"Give."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.04,1:12:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"技术"\N{\fs36}"Technology."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.00,1:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"现在"\N{\fs36}"Now."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.84,1:12:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在干什么\N{\fs36}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.04,1:12:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上尉 10点钟方向\N{\fs36}Captain, on your 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.00,1:12:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止交火 生擒所有反叛人员\N{\fs36}Mutineers are to be apprehended without engaging.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.76,1:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要冒险激怒我们的访客 完毕\N{\fs36}We don't want to risk antagonizing our visitors. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.28,1:12:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安保人员就位 长官 倒计时四分钟\N{\fs36}Security detail inbound, sir. T-minus four minutes remaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.60,1:12:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请指示\N{\fs36}We need to see this through.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.36,1:12:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 听着 子弹上膛\N{\fs36}Okay, this is it. Lock and load.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.00,1:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要守住阵地 拖到任务完成\N{\fs36}We just need to hold them off until it's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.00,1:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到 仅需鸣枪示警 压制火力\N{\fs36}Copy that. Warning shots and suppressive fire only.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.60,1:13:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹上膛 找好掩护\N{\fs36}Load up and get to cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.92,1:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神 避免伤亡\N{\fs36}Stay fresh and we can avoid casualties.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.96,1:13:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abbott想让我写在视镜上\N{\fs36}Abbott wants me to write on the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.32,1:13:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到吗\N{\fs36}Can you even do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.44,1:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs36}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.16,1:14:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法用两只手同时写\N{\fs36}I can't do it with both hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.76,1:15:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.16,1:15:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音\N{\fs36}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.24,1:15:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 走火了  - 在那边\N{\fs36}- Free fire!  - Over there!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.97,1:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被击中了 我被击中了\N{\fs36} I'm hit! I'm hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.08,1:16:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿 慢点起\N{\fs36}Hey, hey, hey. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.76,1:16:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脑部受到了震荡\N{\fs36}You suffered a concussion.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.32,1:16:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躺回去\N{\fs36}Just lay back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.52,1:16:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\fs36}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.80,1:16:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ian怎么样了\N{\fs36}How is Ian?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.28,1:16:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一样 他没事\N{\fs36}Same as you. He's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.84,1:16:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fs36}Who...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.44,1:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁干的\N{\fs36}Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.28,1:16:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些士兵 煽动的电视节目看多了\N{\fs36}Some soldiers. Been watching too much TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.84,1:16:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么动静\N{\fs36}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.36,1:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢点起 慢慢来\N{\fs36}Now, take it easy. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.52,1:16:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个降临点已经不安全了\N{\fs36}The site's no longer secure.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.36,1:17:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在准备撤退\N{\fs36}We're standing by to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.20,1:17:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ian在哪\N{\fs36}Where's Ian?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.84,1:17:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Weber大概10分钟前来过 把他带走了\N{\fs36}Weber came and got him maybe 10 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.72,1:17:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过确认你没事之前 他都不肯离开\N{\fs36}But he wouldn't leave until he knew you were okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.76,1:17:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全营的人都在加班加点\N{\fs36}The whole tent is on the clock
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.94,1:17:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试图破解你们在交流舱得到的信息\N{\fs36}to figure out whatever it is you were given up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.84,1:17:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内容都在这了\N{\fs36}This is all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.88,1:17:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图像传输没有被爆炸打断吗\N{\fs36}The feed wasn't interrupted by the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.88,1:17:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前看来并没有\N{\fs36}Not as far as we can see.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.87,1:17:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看出什么了吗\N{\fs36}You see something?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.24,1:17:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不清楚\N{\fs36}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.04,1:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要召集我的团队和Louise的团队\N{\fs36}I'm gonna need my team to get together with Louise's team.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.56,1:17:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要大家一起研究它\N{\fs36}I need everybody working on this.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.96,1:17:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能离开\N{\fs36}We cannot leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.84,1:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你醒了\N{\fs36}Glad to see you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.12,1:17:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得回交流舱去 和它们说明\N{\fs36}We need to go back in and we need to explain to them
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.06,1:17:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸不是我们造成的\N{\fs36}this wasn't our fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.96,1:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不能再回去了  - 我们得告诉它们 一定得去\N{\fs36}- We can't go back inside. - We have to tell them... We have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.20,1:17:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在"壳"里发生的是一起袭击性事件\N{\fs36}What happened in there was an attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.24,1:17:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以抱最好的希望\N{\fs36}We can hope for the best,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.28,1:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但上头下了命令 让我准备迎接反击\N{\fs36}but I have orders to prepare for retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.24,1:17:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好我们必须得撤\N{\fs36}We may have to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.60,1:17:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这样做是错的 只要它们还在 我们就必须留下\N{\fs36}No, that's the wrong move. As long as they stay, we have to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.28,1:18:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们不打算离开\N{\fs36}Well, they're not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.04,1:18:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么比之前的感觉更糟了\N{\fs36}Why does this feel worse?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.84,1:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中国准备进攻\N{\fs36}China is on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.76,1:18:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正在部署军队\N{\fs36}They're positioning their military
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.15,1:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算一举将外星飞船炸飞\N{\fs36}to blow the alien vessel right out of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.12,1:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情一旦发生\N{\fs36}And if this happens,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.52,1:18:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能坐以待毙 所以做好准备吧\N{\fs36}we can't sit around waiting for retaliation, so get prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.82,1:18:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空军和陆军随时待命\N{\fs36}The Air Force and infantry are standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.40,1:18:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 长官\N{\fs36}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.16,1:19:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚 中国成为首个\N{\fs36}Tonight, China becomes the first world power
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.36,1:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向外星人宣战的世界强国\N{\fs36}to declare war against the aliens.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.52,1:19:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继联合国宣告斡旋失败后\N{\fs36}Following the failure of diplomatic efforts at the United Nations,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.12,1:19:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中方证实 其语言专家已于今晚\N{\fs36}China has confirmed that its language experts have, tonight,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.60,1:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上海降临点向外星人发出了最后通牒\N{\fs36}delivered an ultimatum at the Shanghai site.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.68,1:19:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一段电视声明中 \N{\fs36}In a televised statement,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.14,1:19:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shang将军 中国人民解放军总参谋长\N{\fs36}General Shang, Chairman of the People's Liberation Army,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.12,1:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限外星人在24小时内离开中国领土\N{\fs36}said the aliens have 24 hours to leave Chinese territory
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.88,1:19:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则将面临毁灭性打击\N{\fs36}or face destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.64,1:19:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 他呼吁各国领导人 与中方联合起来\N{\fs36}And he urged all other world leaders to unite with China
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.92,1:19:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统一战线\N{\fs36}and take a similar stance.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.52,1:19:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在降临点附近集结了大批兵力的还包括\N{\fs36}With a huge buildup of forces at their landing sites,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.96,1:19:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴基斯坦 俄罗斯和苏丹\N{\fs36}Pakistan, Russia, and Sudan
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.98,1:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上国家或将响应中方号召\N{\fs36}are thought to be following China's lead.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.64,1:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能毫无规律\N{\fs36}It can't be random.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.04,1:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究它得花好几年时间\N{\fs36}It's going to take us years.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.20,1:20:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那词怎么说来着\N{\fs36}What's this term here?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.08,1:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.97,1:20:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.43,1:20:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\fs36}Sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.24,1:20:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个词怎么说的来着\N{\fs36}What's this term for that thing like a...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.76,1:20:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像专业术语那种\N{\fs36}Like a technical term?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.76,1:20:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是我们达成协议 并且都能从中获利\N{\fs36}Where we make a deal and we both get something out of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.12,1:20:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"妥协"\N{\fs36}"Compromise."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.76,1:20:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs36}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.56,1:20:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点竞争的意思 但是最终双方都能满意\N{\fs36}Like, it's a competition, but both sides end up happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.24,1:20:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着像"双赢"\N{\fs36}Like a win-win.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.24,1:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要更偏理科方面的\N{\fs36}More science-y than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.49,1:20:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想问理科方面的 打电话给你爸\N{\fs36}If you want science, call your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.12,1:21:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs36}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.12,1:21:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs36}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.88,1:21:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我醒了\N{\fs36}It's okay. I'm up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.28,1:21:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会儿什么时候了\N{\fs36}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.49,1:21:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该是你开瓶庆功的时候了\N{\fs36}It's time you open that bottle you've been hiding.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.84,1:21:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有突破了 对不对\N{\fs36}You cracked something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.62,1:21:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你来\N{\fs36}Yeah, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.60,1:21:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个部分\N{\fs36}Take a look at this section.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.48,1:21:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像与时间有关\N{\fs36}It seems to be talking about time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.60,1:21:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们表示"时间"的标记无处不在\N{\fs36}Their symbol for "Time" is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.08,1:21:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 这到底是什么\N{\fs36}So, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.68,1:21:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超光速旅行的公式吗\N{\fs36}A formula for faster-than-light travel?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.80,1:22:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢\N{\fs36}Who can tell?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.27,1:22:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空白太多了\N{\fs36}There are too many gaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.64,1:22:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不完整\N{\fs36}Nothing's complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.16,1:22:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我恍然大悟\N{\fs36}Then it dawned on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.68,1:22:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs36}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.84,1:22:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这儿\N{\fs36}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.32,1:22:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拘泥于有形的部分 也该注意无形的部分 \N{\fs36}Stop focusing on the ones, look at the zeroes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.32,1:22:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面数据占几成 留白又占几成呢\N{\fs36}How much of this is data? How much of it is negative space?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.96,1:22:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就做了个测算\N{\fs36}So, I measured it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.52,1:22:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0.0833 循环\N{\fs36}0.0833 recurring.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.84,1:22:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许化成分数你更熟悉\N{\fs36}Perhaps you'd like that as a fraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.36,1:22:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二分之一\N{\fs36}One of 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.32,1:22:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们要表达的是 这是十二分之一\N{\fs36}What they're saying right here is that this is one of 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.68,1:22:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是整体的其中一部分\N{\fs36}We are part of a larger whole.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.64,1:22:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我们是12名夺奖者之一\N{\fs36}Or we're one of 12 contestants for the prize.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.48,1:22:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非得跟他解释\N{\fs36}Why do I have to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.72,1:22:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在座都是一条心\N{\fs36}We're all working together here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.44,1:22:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得和其他降临点联络\N{\fs36}We need to talk to the other sites.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.24,1:22:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得帮助他们理解\N{\fs36}We need to help them with
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.15,1:22:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们从其他七肢桶那儿得到的信息\N{\fs36}what they've gotten from the other heptapods.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.88,1:22:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能忘了 通讯全被切断了\N{\fs36}In case you don't remember, we're blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.80,1:23:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚中国还威胁说要摧毁那儿的飞船 我们只能自保\N{\fs36}China just threatened to destroy their shell. We're on our own.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.68,1:23:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但根据提示 所有碎片该拼到一起\N{\fs36}Yeah, but this says that all of the pieces fit together.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.56,1:23:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就可以告诉你没人会在乎\N{\fs36}And I'm telling you that no one else cares.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.44,1:23:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个小时前 \N{\fs36}Two hours ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.34,1:23:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从一个俄罗斯加密频道截获了这段音频\N{\fs36}we pulled this audio off a secure channel in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.56,1:23:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个科研团队的人员当时正在对外广播\N{\fs36}Someone on the science team there was broadcasting wide.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.76,1:23:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在俄方的最后一次会话中 外星人说 "没有时间了"\N{\fs36}In their final session, the alien said, "There is no time."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.24,1:23:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"由众化一"\N{\fs36}"Many become one."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.60,1:23:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我们被授予了武器\N{\fs36}I fear we have all been given weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.96,1:23:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人能收到这段话 求你们\N{\fs36}If anyone is receiving this, please...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.48,1:23:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我觉得\N{\fs36}Well, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.15,1:23:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这段话可以翻译成很多不同的意思\N{\fs36}there are a lot of ways you can interpret what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.68,1:23:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要翻译也知道这是什么意思\N{\fs36}I don't need an interpreter to know what this means.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.76,1:23:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯刚刚处决了一名他们自己的专家\N{\fs36}Russia just executed one of their own experts
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.10,1:23:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来保守他们的秘密\N{\fs36}to keep their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.70,1:23:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"由众化一"可能只是它们表达\N{\fs36}"Many become one" could just be their way of saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.08,1:23:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"需要集合"的方式\N{\fs36}"Some assembly required."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.60,1:23:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把信息以碎片的方式传递给我们\N{\fs36}Why hand it out to us in pieces?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.68,1:23:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不直接全部交出来呢\N{\fs36}Why not just give it all over?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.28,1:23:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更好的办法 能逼出人类团结合作的奇迹吗\N{\fs36}Well, what better way to force us to work together for once?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.67,1:23:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我信了你这番话\N{\fs36}Even if I did believe you,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.76,1:24:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又怎么可能说服其他国家来配合我们\N{\fs36}how in the world you gonna get anybody else to play along
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.32,1:24:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者交出他们的数据呢\N{\fs36}or give up their data?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.88,1:24:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以提供我们的成果作为报答\N{\fs36}We offer ours in return.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.72,1:24:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs36}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.98,1:24:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 交易吗\N{\fs36}What, trade?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.27,1:24:10.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(640,80)}非零和博弈是一种合作下的博弈,博弈中各方的收益或损失的总和不是零值,\N使博弈双方存在"双赢"的可能
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.28,1:24:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是场"非零和博弈"\N{\fs36}It's a non-zero sum game.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.81,1:24:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"非零和博弈"\N{\fs36}"Non-zero sum game."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.96,1:24:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它\N{\fs36}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.32,1:24:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦\N{\fs36}Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.24,1:24:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九个降临点基地都彻底切断通讯信号了\N{\fs36}Nine of the landing sites have gone total comms blackout.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.00,1:24:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联络他们的唯一途径是开车过去\N{\fs36}Only way to reach them is to physically drive there
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.25,1:24:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后朝边防守卫大喊 我们已经着手在办了\N{\fs36}and yell at the border guards, which we're doing,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.11,1:24:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样肯定来不及\N{\fs36}but it won't be fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.28,1:24:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定还有别的方法 能把消息传给他们\N{\fs36}There's got to be a way to... To get the message to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.88,1:24:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传给我们的盟友或许还有可能 \N{\fs36}To our allies maybe,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.08,1:24:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过事到如今 回天乏术 已经太迟了\N{\fs36}but at this stage, it's too little too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.88,1:24:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得在某个国家挑起全球战争前\N{\fs36}What we need is to get all the other nations online
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.80,1:24:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织其他国家恢复连线\N{\fs36}before one starts global war,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.64,1:24:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们没办法联系到他们\N{\fs36}and there's no way for us to reach them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.76,1:24:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等一下\N{\fs36}Wait. Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.32,1:24:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有办法啊\N{\fs36}There is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.44,1:24:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我们头顶上\N{\fs36}It's right above us.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.88,1:24:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这办法目前很成问题\N{\fs36}That's problematic for us right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.36,1:24:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五角大楼认定了我们这只"壳"会发动反击\N{\fs36}The Pentagon's convinced our shell will retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.00,1:25:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜一小时内他们就会下令让我们撤离\N{\fs36}My guess is they'll order us to evacuate within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.66,1:25:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 它们不是我们的敌人\N{\fs36}Look, they're not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.08,1:25:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们从未对我们展现过侵略性\N{\fs36}They've made no act of aggression towards us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.88,1:25:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这就是它们侵略的方式\N{\fs36}Maybe this is their way of being aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.92,1:25:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题不在此\N{\fs36}That's not the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.92,1:25:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底有什么问题\N{\fs36}Well, what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.13,1:25:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么把你们弄回交流舱去\N{\fs36}How do we get you back in that room
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.61,1:25:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在它离地半英里了啊\N{\fs36}when it's half a mile straight up?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.68,1:25:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们已经达成使命\N{\fs36}I think our work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.16,1:25:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在该由上头拿主意了\N{\fs36}It's in the hands of our superiors now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.04,1:25:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她这又是搞什么\N{\fs36}What the hell is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.20,1:26:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 天哪 天哪 别\N{\fs36}No. God. Oh, God. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.76,1:29:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Costello吗\N{\fs36}Costello?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.00,1:29:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abbott在哪儿\N{\fs36}Where's Abbott?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.12,1:29:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs36}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.20,1:29:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很抱歉\N{\fs36}We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.88,1:29:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你\N{\fs36}I need you to...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.84,1:29:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你给其他降临点发送一条信息\N{\fs36}I need you to send a message to the other sites.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.64,1:30:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不\N{\fs36}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.48,1:30:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fs36}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.64,1:30:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来这儿的目的是什么\N{\fs36}What is your purpose here?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.84,1:30:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么会知道未来的事\N{\fs36}How can you know the future?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.88,1:31:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不\N{\fs36}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.68,1:31:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fs36}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.00,1:31:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子是谁\N{\fs36}Who is this child?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.00,1:31:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节目的名字叫<妈妈爸爸与动物谈话>\N{\fs36}The show is called Mommy and Daddy Talk to Animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.76,1:31:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs36}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.04,1:31:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等等\N{\fs36}No... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.20,1:32:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Banks博士  - Louise\N{\fs36}- Dr. Banks! - Louise!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.88,1:32:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs36}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.37,1:32:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嘿 你还好吗  - 嗯\N{\fs36}- Hey. You all right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.48,1:32:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 来 怎么了 发生了什么  - 我很好\N{\fs36}- Here, come on. What happened? - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.24,1:32:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想办法理清头绪 这事关重大\N{\fs36}I'm trying to figure it out. This is too big.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.08,1:33:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在都无所谓了 我们已经得令要撤离了\N{\fs36}Doesn't matter now. We have orders to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.96,1:33:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 俄罗斯和苏丹决定站中国那边了\N{\fs36}- Why? - Russia and Sudan are following China.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.16,1:33:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ian 我不明白为什么\N{\fs36}Ian. I don't understand why the...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.40,1:33:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮我 妈妈\N{\fs36}Help me, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.84,1:33:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.16,1:33:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fs36}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.48,1:33:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs36}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.19,1:33:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mama!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.32,1:33:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 亲爱的\N{\fs36}Sorry, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.28,1:33:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是什么日子 你知道吗 宝贝\N{\fs36}What day is it? Do you know, baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.68,1:33:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周日\N{\fs36}Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.75,1:33:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会像爸爸一样离开我吗\N{\fs36}Are you gonna leave me like Daddy did?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.88,1:33:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hannah 亲爱的 你爸爸没有离开你\N{\fs36}Hannah, honey, your daddy didn't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.56,1:33:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这周末就能见到他了\N{\fs36}You're gonna see him this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.92,1:33:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看我的眼神都跟以前不一样了\N{\fs36}He doesn't look at me the same way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.04,1:33:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我犯错了\N{\fs36}That's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.00,1:34:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉了他一些事情 他没做好心理准备\N{\fs36}I told him something that he wasn't ready to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.04,1:34:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事情\N{\fs36}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.52,1:34:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 不管你信不信\N{\fs36}Well, believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.88,1:34:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一些注定会发生的事情\N{\fs36}I know something that's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.72,1:34:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法解释我怎么知道的 我就是知道\N{\fs36}I can't explain how I know. I just do.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.92,1:34:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我告诉你爸爸的时候 他很生气\N{\fs36}And when I told your daddy, he got really mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.92,1:34:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他说我不应该这么做\N{\fs36}And he said I made the wrong choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.08,1:34:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么事情要发生啊\N{\fs36}What? What's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.72,1:34:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一种非常罕见的疾病有关\N{\fs36}It has to do with a really rare disease.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.95,1:34:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是不可阻挡的\N{\fs36}And it's unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.76,1:34:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟你一样\N{\fs36}Kind of like you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.49,1:34:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你游泳的冲劲 你诗歌的灵气\N{\fs36}Your swimming, and your poetry,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.64,1:34:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你给世界带来的那些形形色色的美好\N{\fs36}and all the other amazing things that you share with the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.44,1:35:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不可阻挡的吗\N{\fs36}I am unstoppable?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.16,1:35:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊\N{\fs36}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.28,1:35:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接住你了\N{\fs36}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.48,1:35:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.64,1:35:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.44,1:35:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚才明白过来为什么我丈夫离开了我\N{\fs36}I just realized why my husband left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.16,1:35:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫离开了我\N{\fs36}My husband left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.76,1:35:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你结过婚的吗\N{\fs36}You were married?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.64,1:35:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 我们得赶紧离开这里\N{\fs36}Come on. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.64,1:36:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs36}Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.84,1:36:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs36}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.52,1:36:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我叫Hannah\N{\fs36}Why is my name Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.40,1:36:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 东西都在这里\N{\fs36}Yeah, got it right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.88,1:36:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把那些人召集回来\N{\fs36}Get those people back, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.68,1:36:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你的名字非常特殊 因为它是回文\N{\fs36}Well, your name is very special because it is a palindrome.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.88,1:36:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是顺着念还是倒着念 都是一样的\N{\fs36}It reads the same forward and backward.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.56,1:36:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好了 伙计们 过来给我帮把手  - 明白 长官\N{\fs36}- All right, guys, give me a hand here. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.84,1:36:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个搬到后面去\N{\fs36}That goes in the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.80,1:36:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民间承包商务必携带本人授权胸章\N{\fs36}Civilian contractors must have their authorization badges
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.44,1:36:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和通行证以通过检查\N{\fs36}and passkeys when checking...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.12,1:37:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤离进行中\N{\fs36}Evacuation underway...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.04,1:37:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs36}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.84,1:37:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该离开这儿了\N{\fs36}Look, we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.04,1:37:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要把这个一起带走的\N{\fs36}We're taking this with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.32,1:37:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能读懂了\N{\fs36}I can read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.96,1:37:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我知道这是什么了 - 什么\N{\fs36}- I know what it is. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.84,1:37:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一件武器 这是一件礼物\N{\fs36}It's not a weapon, it's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.72,1:37:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的语言就是它们的武器\N{\fs36}The weapon is their language.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.56,1:37:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们对我们倾囊相授 你明白这意味着什么吗\N{\fs36}They gave it all to us. Do you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.04,1:37:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说我们能学习七肢桶的语言 前提是能逃过这劫\N{\fs36}So we can learn Heptapod, if we survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.80,1:37:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你学了 等你学到一定程度\N{\fs36}If you learn it, when you really learn it,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.76,1:37:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会开始以它们的方式感知时间\N{\fs36}you begin to perceive time the way that they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.24,1:38:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你就能看见未来将会发生什么\N{\fs36}So you can see what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.96,1:38:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它们所感知的时间 与我们的不同\N{\fs36}But time, it isn't the same for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.48,1:38:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是非线性的  - 听着\N{\fs36}- It's non-linear. - Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.80,1:38:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经尽力了 可还是没能挽救\N{\fs36}We did our best, but it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.53,1:38:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跟这位上尉同行\N{\fs36}The captain will load you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.08,1:38:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五分钟之后你们就出发\N{\fs36}You're lifting off in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.04,1:38:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ian 还有Louise 能和你们共事是我的荣幸\N{\fs36}Ian, Louise, it was an honor to work with ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.72,1:38:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们好运\N{\fs36}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.48,1:38:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 上校\N{\fs36}Hey, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.96,1:38:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问问要把我们带哪儿去\N{\fs36}I'm gonna find out where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.64,1:38:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒 妈妈\N{\fs36}Wake up, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.48,1:39:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Banks博士\N{\fs36}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.24,1:39:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸会\N{\fs36}A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.20,1:39:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shang将军\N{\fs36}General Shang.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.40,1:39:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的荣幸才对\N{\fs36}The pleasure is mine, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.92,1:39:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们总统说\N{\fs36}Your President said
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.04,1:39:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很荣幸能请到我来参加庆典\N{\fs36}he was honored to host me at the celebration...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.40,1:39:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 当然  - 但我得承认\N{\fs36}- Yes. - ...but I confess,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.24,1:39:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里只有一个原因\N{\fs36}the only reason why I'm here is to
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.40,1:39:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是亲自见你一面\N{\fs36}meet you in person.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.36,1:39:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见我吗 真是受宠若惊 谢谢\N{\fs36}Me? Well, I'm flattered. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.08,1:39:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18个月前\N{\fs36}Now, 18 months ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.20,1:39:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了一件非同凡响的事\N{\fs36}you did something remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.92,1:39:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的上级都未曾做到的事\N{\fs36}Something not even my superior has done.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.24,1:39:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您指的是\N{\fs36}And what's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.92,1:40:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我改变了心意\N{\fs36}You changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.04,1:40:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场联合是因你而存在\N{\fs36}You're the reason for this unification.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.60,1:40:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都因你打通了我的私人号码而起\N{\fs36}All because you reached out to me on my private number.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.48,1:40:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的私人号码\N{\fs36}Your private number.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.56,1:40:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军 我不知道您的私人号码啊\N{\fs36}General, I don't know your private number.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.44,1:40:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就知道了\N{\fs36}Now you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.32,1:40:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不明白这其中的奥妙\N{\fs36}I do not claim to know how your mind works, but
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.44,1:40:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我相信让你看到我的号码至关重要\N{\fs36}I believe it was important for you to see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.48,1:40:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是给您打电话了 对吗\N{\fs36}I called you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.44,1:40:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 你打了\N{\fs36}Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.84,1:40:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Louise\N{\fs36}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.52,1:41:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好了 咱们把系统全线关闭  - 长官\N{\fs36}- All right, let's shut down the system. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.36,1:41:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有台正在打去中国的卫星电话\N{\fs36}There's a sat-line here dialing China.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.12,1:41:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗 你说的"这里"是哪里\N{\fs36}Here? What do you mean "Here"?
